<plot>Six-year-old Sugar Grey has inherited a ranch, which she will lose to her cousin Jeff Grey is a certain number of cattle aren't delivered on time. Jeff has been working with Vic Insley to steal Sugar's cattle so he can obtain the ranch. Banker Jim Coleman, ranch overseer against Jeff's wishes, hires Tex Wright and Slim Hunkafeller as cowhands on Sugar's ranch. Tex and Slim works nights changing Insley's brand on the rustled cattle from Sugar's herd to yet another brand. Tex then bribes the rustlers to help him herd the cattle to the loading pens. Jeff convinces the Sheriff that Tex is a rustler. Tex eludes the posse and Slim and his men surround the rustlers.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?421186</url></doc>
